00:53:32,160 --> 00:53:34,481
If the artist can't create one out of zero,

764
00:53:34,481 --> 00:53:40,361
no matter which famous PD is by his side, it's no use.

765
00:53:43,780 --> 00:53:45,891
When an artist loses self-confidence

766
00:53:45,891 --> 00:53:50,961
and has to draw something in a situation where they're unsure of anything,

767
00:53:50,961 --> 00:53:53,631
those miserable times...

768
00:53:54,750 --> 00:53:57,221
are probably impossible for us to even imagine.

769
00:54:01,190 --> 00:54:06,081
Try talking it out once more with Artist Sin Dae Ryuk.

770
00:54:06,081 --> 00:54:07,551
Okay.

771
00:54:17,390 --> 00:54:20,331
You're really disappointed in me, aren't you?

772
00:54:21,400 --> 00:54:23,911
I'm still expecting great things, too.

773
00:54:31,331 --> 00:54:33,461
Would you like to come in?

774
00:54:33,461 --> 00:54:36,561
No, I'll just end up disturbing his peace.

775
00:54:36,561 --> 00:54:42,391
D-Dae Ryuk finally ate your food after a few days.

776
00:54:42,391 --> 00:54:45,401
That's such a relief!

777
00:54:45,401 --> 00:54:47,751
I should've brought more.

778
00:54:51,371 --> 00:54:52,971
Please...

779
00:54:52,971 --> 00:54:56,021
Please take good care of my Dae Ryuk.

780
00:55:02,581 --> 00:55:07,961
You should enjoy the food, too.

781
00:55:07,961 --> 00:55:09,883
All right.

782
00:55:39,171 --> 00:55:42,406
Hey, what are you doing? Stop it!

783
00:55:42,406 --> 00:55:43,742
What are you doing?

784
00:55:43,742 --> 00:55:46,442
That woman brought this, didn't she?

785
00:55:49,816 --> 00:55:51,906
Hey, hey, hey, hey!

786
00:55:55,643 --> 00:55:58,206
PD On, now really isn't a good time.

787
00:55:58,206 --> 00:55:59,936
Why?

788
00:55:59,936 --> 00:56:02,646
That woman came here again.

789
00:56:02,646 --> 00:56:04,856
Your mother did?

790
00:56:09,216 --> 00:56:12,816
