791
00:56:13,676 --> 00:56:16,406
I don't even want to know.

792
00:56:16,406 --> 00:56:18,426
I need to tell you something about your mother.

793
00:56:18,426 --> 00:56:22,296
- I said I don't want to know!
 - There's a reason...

794
00:56:23,466 --> 00:56:26,896
why your mother came looking for you after all this time.

795
00:56:29,056 --> 00:56:32,266
Your mother has Alzheimer's.

796
00:56:35,086 --> 00:56:36,816
And one more thing.

797
00:56:36,816 --> 00:56:39,856
There's something you're not aware of.

798
00:56:42,306 --> 00:56:44,286
What is it?

799
00:56:48,466 --> 00:56:53,736
A long time ago, she said there was a fire in your house.

800
00:56:59,396 --> 00:57:00,136
