806
00:57:09,026 --> 00:57:10,956
 Dae Ryuk's mom! There's big trouble! There's big trouble! 

807
00:57:10,956 --> 00:57:13,916
 Your house is on fire! 

808
00:57:13,916 --> 00:57:16,966
