00:57:35,706 --> 00:57:38,176
 Dae Ryuk! 

817
00:57:38,176 --> 00:57:40,256
 D-Dae Ryuk! 

818
00:57:41,446 --> 00:57:43,876
 Are you okay? 

819
00:57:44,646 --> 00:57:47,026
 My sketchbook... 

820
00:57:47,026 --> 00:57:48,816
 Okay. 

821
00:57:50,696 --> 00:57:52,666
 Ow, it's hot! 

822
00:58:05,600 --> 00:58:09,300
 Don't go near the kitchen. Do you know? 

823
00:58:21,996 --> 00:58:24,816
 I'll be back soon after work, 

824
00:58:24,816 --> 00:58:30,166
