825
00:58:30,166 --> 00:58:32,826
 I'll be back soon, okay? 

826
00:59:02,456 --> 00:59:07,716
Why didn't you tell him about that?

827
00:59:07,716 --> 00:59:10,726
I'm not sure if it's because of the shock.

828
00:59:10,726 --> 00:59:14,646
