831
00:59:22,336 --> 00:59:24,256
But...

832
00:59:25,136 --> 00:59:27,696
It's my fault.

833
00:59:28,546 --> 00:59:34,066
Leaving that young child alone like that.

834
00:59:35,066 --> 00:59:38,386
There's nothing wrong with his resentment.

835
00:59:39,036 --> 00:59:42,816
